cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.DC

This paper deals with the analysis of malware in Android devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves the analysis of application behavior, which can be related to software engineering (cs.SE) and system integration (cs.SI). The use of indicators such as CPU usage and RAM usage can be related to cyber-physical systems (cs.CY) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
